---
---
<!-- ScoreImmo - Outils gratuits -->
<section class="si-section" style="padding:3rem 0;">
  <div class="si-container" style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2rem;">
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:2rem;">
      <span style="display:inline-block;background:rgba(59,130,246,0.1);color:#3B82F6;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:20px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:12px;">Gratuit</span>
      <h2 style="font-family:var(--si-font-heading);font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:800;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Outils gratuits pour ton projet immobilier</h2>
      <p style="color:#64748B;font-size:1rem;margin:0;">Calcule, simule, décide en confiance.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));gap:16px;">
      <a href="/pages/calculateur-frais-de-notaire" class="si-outils-card" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);border-radius:16px;padding:24px;text-decoration:none;color:#0F172A;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);transition:transform 0.2s,box-shadow 0.2s;">
        <span style="font-size:2rem;display:block;margin-bottom:12px;">🧮</span>
        <p style="font-family:var(--si-font-heading);font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;margin:0 0 6px;">Frais de notaire</p>
        <p style="color:#64748B;font-size:0.875rem;margin:0 0 16px;line-height:1.5;">Estime tes frais de notaire par département. Barème 2026 officiel.</p>
        <span style="color:#3B82F6;font-weight:600;font-size:0.875rem;">Calculer →</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/pages/calculateur-capacite-emprunt" class="si-outils-card" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);border-radius:16px;padding:24px;text-decoration:none;color:#0F172A;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);transition:transform 0.2s,box-shadow 0.2s;">
        <span style="font-size:2rem;display:block;margin-bottom:12px;">💰</span>
        <p style="font-family:var(--si-font-heading);font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;margin:0 0 6px;">Capacité d'emprunt</p>
        <p style="color:#64748B;font-size:0.875rem;margin:0 0 16px;line-height:1.5;">Calcule combien tu peux emprunter (règle HCSF 35%).</p>
        <span style="color:#3B82F6;font-weight:600;font-size:0.875rem;">Calculer →</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/pages/calculateur-mensualite-credit" class="si-outils-card" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);border-radius:16px;padding:24px;text-decoration:none;color:#0F172A;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);transition:transform 0.2s,box-shadow 0.2s;">
        <span style="font-size:2rem;display:block;margin-bottom:12px;">📊</span>
        <p style="font-family:var(--si-font-heading);font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;margin:0 0 6px;">Mensualité crédit</p>
        <p style="color:#64748B;font-size:0.875rem;margin:0 0 16px;line-height:1.5;">Simule tes mensualités selon la durée et le taux.</p>
        <span style="color:#3B82F6;font-weight:600;font-size:0.875rem;">Calculer →</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/pages/calculateur-rendement-locatif" class="si-outils-card" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);border-radius:16px;padding:24px;text-decoration:none;color:#0F172A;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);transition:transform 0.2s,box-shadow 0.2s;">
        <span style="font-size:2rem;display:block;margin-bottom:12px;">📈</span>
        <p style="font-family:var(--si-font-heading);font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;margin:0 0 6px;">Rendement locatif</p>
        <p style="color:#64748B;font-size:0.875rem;margin:0 0 16px;line-height:1.5;">Calcule le rendement brut, net et net-net de ton investissement.</p>
        <span style="color:#3B82F6;font-weight:600;font-size:0.875rem;">Calculer →</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<style>
  .si-outils-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1) !important; }
</style>
